---
title: Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto and Spinach Penne with Marinated Mozzarella and Garlic Ciabatta
description: If it ain't broke, don't fix it. The old adage rings true in this classic combination of spinach and sun-dried tomatoes with creamy pasta and marinated mozzarella. It's a richly satisfying meal that will bring a touch of freshness to your dinner table!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pennes-au-pesto-de-tomates-sechees-et-aux-epinards-46f13aa4.jpg
